org.apache.paimon.annotation

Annotation Type Documentation.ExcludeFromDocumentation


  • @Target(value={FIELD,TYPE})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public static @interface Documentation.ExcludeFromDocumentation
    Annotation used on config option fields or REST API message headers to exclude it from documentation.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String value
      The optional reason why it is excluded from documentation.

    • Element Detail

      • value

        public abstract String value
        The optional reason why it is excluded from documentation.
        Default:
        ""
